iki.php/Main/EyePoke">Eye Poke</a>: Shouko does this to Yuuji anytime she doesn't want him looking at other women, which is practically all the time.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FacelessMasses" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FacelessMasses">Faceless Masses</a>: Anyone who doesn't have a name is represented with their class letter. Double points for evoking <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FacelessGoons" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FacelessGoons">Faceless Goons</a> with the FFF, who just need to change into a black KKK-like robe.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FailureIsTheOnlyOption" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FailureIsTheOnlyOption">Failure Is the Only Option</a>: If they ever won against Class A, what would be the point of the series?<ul><li> Most things Akihisa says or some of his plans; <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/IndyPloy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/IndyPloy">on some occasions, however...</a></li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FeminineWomenCanCook" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FeminineWomenCanCook">Feminine Women Can Cook</a>: Strongly subverted. Mizuki is quite feminine and can make <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FoodPorn" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FoodPorn">visually astounding meals</a>. But <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LethalChef" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LethalChef">just smelling her food is enough to induce nightmares</a>. For another layer of subversion, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Tomboy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Tomboy">Minami</a> has been shown to cook elaborate bentos and <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SupremeChef" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SupremeChef">no complaints have been made so far about her food</a>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FestivalEpisode" title="/pmwiki/p